Nisus invests Rs. 30 cr in Shriram Landâ€™s projects


Nisus Finance Services Co. Pvt. Ltd. (NiFCO) has invested Rs.30 crore in Bengaluru-based Shriram Land Development for funding its residential projects at Anekal, near Electronics City. The money was raised through issue of non-convertible debentures. The projects involve developing residential plots and affordable apartments totalling a million sq. ft, according to a statement from the companies.

